Vsftpd is a major ftp server, kernel.org uses vsftpd

== Installation ==
Install {{Package|net-ftp/vsftpd}}:
{{Emerge|vsftpd}}

=== daemon ===

open-rc
{{RootCmd|rc-update add vsftpd default}}
systemd
{{RootCmd|systemctl enable vsftpd}}

==== anon access ====

{{RootCmd|mkdir /home/ftp}}

{{File|/etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf||<pre>
listen=YES
local_enable=NO
anonymous_enable=YES
write_enable=NO
anon_root=/home/ftp</pre>}}

